title: 223. Pressure To Productivity
itunes:title: 223. Pressure To Productivity
description: In today's episode, Andy talks about how society will push you towards comfort to keep you from realizing your full potential, how you can become comfortable being uncomfortable, and why you should welcome pressure and turn it into productive action.
